Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:18.22,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰も彼もが{\fscx85}Rival{\fscx100} 混沌の{\fscx85}Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.70,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscx75\blur3}Hide and seek so dangerous night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.56,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Tick tick tack 時計仕掛け above the 摩天楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.60,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}そっと忍ばす {\fscx75}My heart is a trap and bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:34.90,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}Ah-ah-ah 群がる視線を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:35.94,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Who's the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.16,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}勝負は一度きり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.26,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今 火を点けて
