Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.14,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 150)\blur3\fs30\fsp-3}Feel it now, feel it now, feel it now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.28,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導火線の行方は風まかせ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.08,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命の{\fscx75}Countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:06.10,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜风也茫然不解的旋律正在吹响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:10.60,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这既不是笑谈也不是游戏 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:18.22,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他人皆是对手 混沌的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.70,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}躲猫猫 如此危险的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.56,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘀嗒嘀嗒 摩天楼上时钟作响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.60,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄然隐匿的 我心如陷阱与炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:34.90,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊啊 脱离成群的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:35.94,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸存者会是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.16,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胜负仅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.26,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 点燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:48.72,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多赐予
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.70,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盗走前 你看 爱在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.96,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感触到了热气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:05:00.14,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.14,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.28,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导火线的行踪就承载于风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.08,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命运的倒计时
